  m_text: "Welcome to Dawn of the Hollow Core.\n\nYou guard the Core \u2014 the last
    thing holding this world together. If it is destroyed, everything resets.\n\nDay
    is for preparation. At night, creatures attack both you and the Core. Stronger
    enemies are found in deeper areas, not later nights.\n\nOn the 20th night, a
    boss will appear. Defeat it to move closer to the truth.\n\nProtect the Core.
    Survive."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 5c59a69e0bd8a5440a269336220c61e1, type: 2}
